  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Importing and exporting waste if there’s no Brexit deal
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What UK waste importers and exporters must do to prepare for changes to rules around notified waste shipments if the UK leaves the EU with no deal.</p>

  </div>
</div>

